ActAnti-terrorism Act, 2015
SubjectOrder Fixing July 1, 2015 and August 1, 2015 as the Days on which Certain Provisions of the Act Come into Force
PrecisOrder fixing (1) July 1, 2015 as the day on which Part 5 of the ANTI-TERRORISM ACT, 2015, chapter 20 of the Statutes of Canada 2015, COMES INTO FORCE; and (2) August 1, 2015 as the day on which sections 2 to 8 and 11 to 13 of the ANTI-TERRORISM ACT, 2015, COMES INTO FORCE.
